snippet.title: Dark Deception: Monsters & Mortals - Monstrum DLC Trailer
snippet.description:
Dark Deception: Monsters & Mortals - Monstrum DLC is available on Steam Dec 21st @noon PST! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1450740/Monsters__Mortals__Monstrum
Dark Deception: Monsters & Mortals is available on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1266690/Dark_Deception_Monsters__Mortals/

Join this channel to get access to perks:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCUtLsKBsHJSC4xJRdI-i5Eg/join
